---
import LoanProductLayout from "@/layouts/LoanProductLayout.astro";
const title = "Small Business Loans";
const subtitle = "Get the right small business loan for your needs. Small business loans help SMEs manage cash flow, invest in growth, and cover one-off costs. Compare options from multiple lenders and apply in minutes.";
---
<LoanProductLayout title={title} subtitle={subtitle} updatedAt="November 2025">
  
  <!-- What is a small business loan -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">What is a small business loan?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      A small business loan is a type of finance designed to help businesses with fewer employees or lower turnover access funding. The loan can be used to cover working capital, manage cash flow, invest in growth, or handle unexpected expenses.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
      Unlike personal loans, small business loans are assessed on your company's trading history, revenue, and credit profile. They provide flexible funding solutions tailored to the unique needs of small and medium-sized enterprises.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">How do small business loans work?</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Apply through lender or broker</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">You apply through a lender or broker such as Runway.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Lender assesses your business</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">The lender assesses your business credit score, trading history, and affordability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Receive lump sum</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">If approved, you'll receive a lump sum which you repay in fixed instalments (plus interest) over an agreed term.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">4</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Repay over term</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Repayments can be daily, weekly, or monthly depending on the lender. Terms typically range from 3 months to 5 years.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Types of small business loans -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Types of small business loans</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Unsecured business loans</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">No collateral required, based on your credit profile. Ideal for businesses without assets to secure against.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Secured business loans</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Backed by assets such as property or equipment. Often offer better rates and higher amounts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Government-backed loans</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">For example, government guarantee schemes. May offer more favorable terms for eligible businesses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Short-term loans</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Flexible borrowing for cash flow. Typically repaid over 3-12 months for immediate needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Medium-term loans</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Repaid over 1-5 years for growth investments, equipment purchases, or expansion plans.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Long-term loans</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Extended repayment terms of 5+ years for major investments, property purchases, or large-scale expansion.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Common use cases -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Common use cases</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Working capital</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Cover day-to-day operational costs, payroll, and supplier payments during cash flow gaps.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Business expansion</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Fund growth initiatives, open new locations, or enter new markets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Equipment and assets</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Purchase machinery, vehicles, technology, or other business assets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Inventory purchases</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Buy stock ahead of peak seasons or bulk purchase to secure better prices.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Marketing and advertising</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Invest in campaigns, digital marketing, or brand development to grow your customer base.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Unexpected expenses</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Cover emergency repairs, legal fees, or other unforeseen costs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Is it right for your business -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Is it right for your business?</h2>
    
    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50 mb-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Small business loans are suitable for:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) with established trading history</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Businesses needing flexible funding for various purposes</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Companies with regular revenue and cash flow</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Businesses looking for predictable repayment schedules</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Companies needing funds quickly for time-sensitive opportunities</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        It may not be suitable for very new startups without trading history, businesses with poor credit, or companies unable to demonstrate affordability for repayments.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        Startups may be better suited to government schemes, equity finance, or specialized business loans for new businesses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Eligibility -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">Eligibility for a small business loan</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Lenders typically assess several key factors when evaluating small business loan applications:
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Time trading</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Some lenders require 6–12 months of trading history, though requirements vary by provider.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Turnover and profitability</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Minimum annual turnover requirements and evidence of profitability or positive cash flow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Credit profile</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Business and personal credit scores, though some lenders offer bad credit business loans.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Security (for secured loans)</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Whether you can provide security such as property, equipment, or personal guarantees.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Advantages and disadvantages -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Advantages and disadvantages of small business loans</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Advantages</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Access to fast funding for growth or cash flow</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Wide choice of lenders and products</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Predictable repayment schedules</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Flexible use of funds for various business needs</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Can help build business credit history</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Disadvantages</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Interest and fees vary depending on risk profile</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Some lenders require security or personal guarantees</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Missing repayments can impact your credit score</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Total cost can be significant over longer terms</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Application process may require detailed documentation</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How Runway works -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">How to apply with Runway</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">No fees for comparing</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">No fees for comparing and no obligation to proceed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Tell us about your business</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Tell us about your business and the funding you need.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Compare tailored offers</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Compare tailored offers from multiple lenders.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">4</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Provide documents</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Provide documents for underwriting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">5</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Receive funds</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Finalise your facility and receive funds quickly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Can a startup get a small business loan?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Yes - but lenders often require at least 6 months' trading. Startups may be better suited to government schemes, equity finance, or business loans for new businesses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Do I need a good credit score?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Not always. While a strong credit history improves your options, there are bad credit business loans available. Some lenders specialize in working with businesses that have less-than-perfect credit.</p>
      </div>
